cused on achieving team results (using various coaching tools)\",\"Teaching Agile approaches and tools to teams, helping with their implementation in everyday work\",\"Facilitating various team/tribe level ceremonies\",\"Motivating the team for continuous development, forming an atmosphere of trust, respect and support\"],\"requirements\":[\"3-6 years of experience\",\"Knowledge of flexible frameworks (SCRUM, Kanban method) and scaling frameworks (SAFe, LeSS, Nexus)\",\"Knowledge and ability to apply engineering practices (for example, CI, CD, pair programming, TDD, etc.)\",\"Experience in developing short-term and long-term training programs\",\"Public speaking experience\",\"Experience in a development team (in any role)\",\"Knowledge and ability to apply various process/product practices (e.g. Value Stream Mapping, Impact Mapping, Story Mapping, Design Thinking, Lean Startup, Customer Development)\"],\"conditions\":[\"Office near Arbatskaya, Biblioteka Im Lenina metro stations\",\"VHI + dental services\",\"Corporate discounts for employees of the 0z Corp Group\",\"Corporate fitness scheme\",\"Preferential credit scheme\"]}','Agile Coach','Agile Coach','2020-03-31 04:39:26',1000,0),
