, </li><li>ООО «Вебинар технологии», зарегистрированному по адресу: Российская Федерация, 127055, г. Москва, Приютский пер., д.3, стр.1, обработки своих персональных данных на основании заключенного с Оператором договора, в целях участия Пользователя в онлайн-мероприятиях в формате «вебинаров», </li></ul> <p>Настоящим Пользователь подтверждает, что представленные им персональные данные достоверны.</p><p>В случае изменения персональных данных Пользователь обязуется направлять актуальные персональные данные в адрес Оператора или самостоятельно актуализировать их в настройках учетной записи на ресурсе по адресу в сети Интернет: <a href=\"https://portal.woinc.space/client/settings\" target=\"_blank\">https://portal.woinc.space/client/settings</a> (для Пользователей, имеющих доступ к услугам Оператора посредством использования интернет-платформы на ресурсе <a href=\"https://woinc.space\">https://woinc.space</a>).</p><p>Настоящим Пользователь уведомлен, что обработка его персональных данных осуществляется с использованием средств автоматизации, в том числе в информационно-телекоммуникационных сетях.</p><p>Настоящим Пользователь проинформирован о том, что Политика обработки предоставляемых им персональных данных размещена по ссылке <a href=\"https://woinc.space/agreement\">https://woinc.space/agreement</a>.</p><p>Согласие вступает в силу с момента выражения Пользователем согласия на обработку персональных данных путем проставления признака согласия в чекбоксе рядом с текстом Согласия на обработку персональных данных в графическом интерфейсе Сервиса и действует до достижения целей обработки персональных данных или до момента его отзыва.</p><p>Согласие может быть отозвано Пользователем в любое время на странице сайта <a href=\"https://woinc.space/legal-information\">https://woinc.space/legal-information</a>. При этом оказание Услуг, предоставление Сервисов Пользователю на Сайте, а также посредством использования интернет-платформы Оператора на ресурсе woinc.space может быть прекращено.</p><p>В случае отзыва Пользователем настоящего Согласия Оператор вправе продолжить обработку персональных данных Пользователя без его согласия в случаях, порядке и объеме, предусмотренных Федеральным законом от 27 июля 2006 года № 152-ФЗ «О персональных данных».</p></div></section>','<section class=\"agreement\"> <div class=\"container\"> <h1>Consent to personal data processing</h1> <p class=\"agreement__text\">Hereby You (\"<strong>the User</strong>\"), according to the Federal Law \"on Personal Data” No. 152-FZ dated 27.07.2006, voluntary, by your own free will and in your own interest, grant your consent to <strong>Cloud technology Ltd</strong> (\"<strong>the Operator</strong>\"), registered at room 1.207, b.1., 23 Vavilov Street, Moscow, 117312, Russian Federation and Partners of Cloud technology Ltd as defined in Personal Data Processing Policy, to process your personal data, including its collection, recording, systematization, accumulation, storage, verification (updating, modification), retrieval, use and transfer (provision and access) to third parties when its defined by law, to depersonalization, blockage, deletion, destruction of your personal data: first name, last name, postal address, mobile telephone number, job title, company name, e-mail, name of the product/service purchased and its value, purchase history.</p><article class=\"agreement__item\"> <h4 class=\"agreement__sub-title\">Purposes of the personal data processing:</h4> <ul> <li> <p>enhancement of Services provided and its usability, development of new services;</p></li><li> <p>provision of Services under contracts concluded between the Operator and the User, or between the Operator and the legal entity, acting on behalf of the User;</p></li><li> <p>providing access to Services of the Operator after the User filed a request to access the internet platform on the Site of the Operator;</p></li><li> <p>conducting marketing activities (special offers, polls, researches, contests, lotteries) through customer service of the Operator;</p></li><li> <p>communication with the User (notifications, letters, requests) regarding Services provided, performance of the contracts concluded, processing the User’s requests;</p></li><li> <p>provision of an information regarding Services provided by the Operator, development of new products and services. The information might be provided through web-forms of the Site, API, webpages of the Operator on internet platforms and sites of Partners;</p></li><li> <p>providing the User with informational or/and advertisement message (including targeted ads) about Services, events in a business life of the Operator, events organized by the Operator or/and Partners for customers or/and potential customers (seminars, conferences, webinars, special offers, lotteries), about goods, services of Partners and third parties;</p></li><li> <p>conducting statistical and other researchers based on depersonalized data.</p></li></ul> <p>According to the article 3 of the Federal Law \"on Personal Data\" No. 152-FZ dated 27.07.2006, the User hereby grants his/her consent to <strong>entrust</strong> procession of his/her personal data to Carrot Quest LLC, registered at 35a-88, Turgenev Street, Perm, 614107, Russian Federation. The procession of personal data stated in this paragraph is carried out under the contract between the Operator and Carrot Quest LLC for following purposes:</p><ul> <li> <p>enhancement of Services provided by the Operator and its usability, development of new services;</p></li><li> <p>creation of informational and analytical reports and data bases which cannot be transferred to third parties.</p></li></ul> <p>According to the article 3 of the Federal Law \"on Personal Data\" No. 152-FZ dated 27.07.2006, the User hereby grants his/her consent to <strong>entrust</strong> procession of his/her personal data to Webinar Technologies LLC, registered at 3, Bldg. 1, Priyutsky lane, Moscow, 127055, Russian Federation. The procession of personal data stated in this paragraph is carried out under the contract between the Operator and Webinar Technologies LLC for following purposes:</p><ul> <li> <p>User participation in online events in the format of \"webinars\".</p></li></ul> <p>The User hereby confirms that his/her personal data is accurate and valid.</p><p>If personal data of the User is changed, the User undertakes to update it in the settings of the User’s account (<a href=\"https://portal.woinc.space/client/settings\">https://portal.woinc.space/client/settings</a>).</p><p>The User hereby informed, that the policy on User’s Personal Data Processing is located at <a href=\"https://woinc.space/agreement\">https://woinc.space/agreement</a>.</p><p>The Consent to personal data processing is effective since checkbox, which is located at graphical interface, next to the Consent to personal data processing, is checked by the User and valid until purposes of the data procession is fulfilled or until the moment the consent is withdrawn by the User. </p><p>The User may withdraw the Consent at any time by filing written notice on such withdrawal to the Operator, but in such event, the Service provision, access to the Service through the use of the Operator’s internet-platform (woinc.space) might be terminated.</p><p>If the Consent is withdrawn by the User, the Operator is entitled to continue to process the User’s personal data, strictly as it is defined in the Federal Law \"on Personal Data” No. 152-FZ dated 27.07.2006.</p></article> </div></section>',0,'2020-05-15 11:44:10'),
